==English==

===Noun phrase===
''a'' '''[[piece]] of [[furniture]]''' (''plural'' '''[[pieces of furniture]]''')

# An item of furniture; any item, such as a table or cupboard, that consistutes furniture.

====Usage notes====
The phrases '''item of furniture''' and '''piece of furniture''' are used as the singular of the mass noun ''[[furniture]]'', which has no singular of its own.

